"# Linear Regression from First Principles: Wine Quality Prediction\n",
"\n",
"This notebook demonstrates how to build a Linear Regression model from scratch using only NumPy. We will:\n",
"1. Load the Wine Quality dataset using the Hugging Face Data Connector.\n",
"2. Preprocess the data (Scaling and Bias addition).\n",
"3. Implement the Gradient Descent algorithm from first principles.\n",
"4. Provide an interactive interface for users to input wine features and get a quality prediction."
]
},
{
"cell_type": "code",
"execution_count": 1,
"id": "b1e7f383",
"metadata": {
"id": "b1e7f383"
},
"outputs": [],
